articles.description: Adol Christin's next adventure hits PS4 on February 2, Switch and PC in summer 2021Next up for Ys series protagonist Adol Christin is the journey that awaits in Ys IX: Monstrum Nox, and you can see what's in store in NIS America's new English story trailer af…
